{"tid":484142,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解連續三日夢到你","createTime":"2017-11-29T21:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T02:53:27.000Z","uid":35106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"933828ea8b1baa1040dee4ed9f3a57f0f85ead1e","tid":484142,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T21:22:05.000Z","msg":"點解夢入面大家咁親切<br />\n你唔再討厭我 你解封左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂 成年半無傾無見啦<br />\n呢年半過得好頹 又多野發生<br />\n其實當日寧願淡出你身邊範圍<br />\n唔好選擇做一啲令你會好憎我既野<br />\n而自己都控制到心情 <br />\n就算無可能 都唔會搞成今日結果<br />\n不過我諗你忘記左我了<br />\n我存在令你咁困擾 令你咁煩<br />\n<br />\n但可唔可以唔好再出現我夢境呀"},{"pid":"c0979e56bc2fa30717aaec238b5f5e54509b61be","tid":484142,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T21:36:51.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"dafd2b31c5e642deaa5cb3137f9ab71c5783f312","tid":484142,"uid":10544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T21:43:01.000Z","msg":"唔好再令我諗起你好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfb041a339ebf8c82e7c74526024533208412c0","tid":484142,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T22:20:09.000Z","msg":"知你夢到我啦"},{"pid":"8d7af2c77de20c8784d7f358b1dc211eb3101cf8","tid":484142,"uid":127033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"Facebook?"},{"pid":"4bb2c72c85879602fecd4740ded19d807c8ef4ee","tid":484142,"uid":70629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T02:53:27.000Z","msg":"點解我覺得自己識妳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}